<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 24 May 2026</p>

<h2>Who we are</h2>
<p>
  Steve Roberts is the controller for personal data processed through this
  website. You can reach me through the <a href="/contact/">contact page</a> or
  via the details listed there.
</p>

<h2>What we collect</h2>
<p>
  This site does not currently run a contact form or account system. We may
  collect the following data when you visit or contact us:
</p>
<ul>
  <li>Basic server logs from the hosting platform</li>
  <li>Analytics data, if you choose to accept analytics cookies</li>
  <li>Any information you send by email or through external services</li>
</ul>

<h2>How we use data</h2>
<p>We use personal data only to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Respond to direct enquiries</li>
  <li>Keep the site secure and working reliably</li>
  <li>Understand how the site is used, if analytics is enabled and accepted</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="cookies">Cookies</h2>
<p>
  If analytics is enabled for this site, a cookie is used to remember whether
  you accepted or declined analytics. Accepting analytics may also allow Google
  Analytics to set its own cookies for measurement purposes.
</p>
<p>
  You can change your choice at any time using the <a href="/privacy/#cookies"
  >cookie preferences</a>
  link in the footer.
</p>

<h2>Retention</h2>
<p>
  We keep personal data only for as long as needed for the purpose it was
  collected. Hosting logs and analytics data are retained according to the
  relevant provider's default retention settings.
</p>

<h2>Your rights</h2>
<p>
  Under UK GDPR you may ask for access to, correction of, or deletion of your
  personal data where applicable. You can also object to processing based on
  legitimate interests.
</p>

<h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
<p>
  This page may be updated from time to time. Any material changes will be
  reflected here with a new update date. Continued use of this website after any
  changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>
  For privacy questions, use the <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.
</p>
</PageLayout>
